            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                <h4 class="pb-0">Usually Accepted for warranty:</h4>
                <ul class="mt-2 mb-2" style="list-style-type:disc;">
                    <li>Delamination.</li>
                    <li>Problems with Inserts.</li>
                    <li>Cracked topsheet (outside of the binding area and if the woodcore is not broken).</li>
                    <li>Split edge from sidewall (if there is no obvious impact on the edge).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                <h4 class="pb-0">Probably Declined for Warranty:</h4>
                <ul class="mt-2 mb-2" style="list-style-type:disc;">
                    <li>Any damage on the base due to impact.</li>
                    <li>Broken edges due to impact.</li>
                    <li>A completely broken board.</li>
                    <li>Screws pushed through the base (use of inserts screws that are too long, or used without a washer).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
      
