                    <li>You are covered with a limited lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects on Baseplates, Disks, Heelhoops and Highbacks.</li>
                    <li>You are covered against manufacturing defects only under normal use, and when set up as instructed by the manual.</li>
                    <li>You are NOT covered for cosmetic damage, like scratches or dents, or normal wear and tear.</li>
                    <li>You are NOT covered for damage caused by misuse, collision, alteration or modification.</li>
                    <li>You are NOT covered for damage caused by improper assembly or installation. Please read the manual carefully!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
      
